description: One is a Catholic social conservative, the other a pro-LGBT mayor. Who will win on Sunday?
title: Duda vs Trzaskowski: The fight for Poland's future
title_page: Duda vs Trzaskowski: The fight for Poland's future - BBC News
maintext: If the more liberal mayor of Warsaw, Rafal Trzaskowski, wins, he has said he will stand up for minorities and use the president's right to veto legislation to block what he sees as the government's attempts to politicise the judiciary and attack democratic values.
